 hw/block/nvme.h       |   5 ++
 hw/block/trace-events |   5 ++
 include/block/nvme.h  | 172 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
 4 files changed, 346 insertions(+), 1 deletion(-)

